  List of Awesome Stylized Movies to Watch

One of the best ways to learn filmmaking is to simply watch really great films. I want to encourage you to take some time to watch films that feature great storytelling, cinematography, and performance. Sometimes these films aren't 'easy' to watch, but their deeper narratives and thoughtfulness can lead to some incredible creative inspiration.

You can start at the top of the list and work your way down, but honestly every film in there is fantastic.
